added.title: Magic Man
added.description: In a quest to become a magic man, Beast Boy accidentally destroys Raven's spell book, so they must go find another one.

added.title: Titans Go Casual
added.description: The Superhero Board of Authority institutes a dress code which leads the Titans to introduce Casual Tuesday.

added.title: Rain on Your Wedding Day
added.description: While facing off with The Brain, Robin tries to teach the other Titans the proper definition of irony.

added.title: Teen Titans Roar!
added.description: The Titans are outraged when their favorite cartoon is rebooted so they come up with a plan to get this new show off the air.

added.title: The Horror of Hook Mountain
added.description: Tygra takes Lion-O climbing up the peak of Hook Mountain to teach him a lesson about trust. But when they get trapped by a snowstorm and take refuge in a creepy cabin owned by the creepy Snowman - it's Tygra's ability to the trust that's gonna be tested.

added.title: ThunderSlobs
added.description: Tygra's feeling unappreciated by the other ThunderCats so he starts hanging out with Mumm-Ra and cleaning his Black Pyramid?! Whaaaaaaat?

added.title: Panthro Plagiarized!
added.description: Vultureman has got a brand new invention but there's one big problem: he stole the idea from Panthro! Oh, also Vultureman is using his invention to take over Third Earth. So, there are two big problems.

added.title: Warrior Maiden Invasion
added.description: Third Earth is being overrun by super tough, super buff Warrior Maidens and it looks like the ThunderCats are next on their hit list! It's gonna be up to the ThunderKittens to save the day even though the kittens are so small and the Warrior Maidens are so big.

added.title: Lost Sword
added.description: Lion-O is reminded that he needs to plug the Sword of Omens into the Cats' Lair each night or else the base will run out of power. That's fine, it's not like Lion-O's going to accidentally lose the sword or anything. Right?

added.title: Lie-Ranosaurus Wrecked
added.description: Owen pretends to be Izzy's pet dinosaur after leading her to believe she dug him up in the school playground.

added.title: A Ninjustice to Harold
added.description: Harold's world is turned upside down when Beth becomes the class ninja.

added.title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
added.description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

added.title: Hic Hic Hooray
added.description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

added.title: Party Poopers
added.description: Ben completely ignores Gwen when she takes him to a family fun center. Meanwhile, Frightwig pushes Zombozo back into a life of crime after he ends up becoming a party clown. Now, both Ben and Zombozo will have to learn that you shouldn't ignore your friends!

added.title: Wind Some, Lose Some
added.description: At the Mojave Wind Farm in Texas, Max and Gwen plan to set Ben straight on his kooky ideas about how wind works, but when they find the Weatherheads using the towering turbines for their latest nefarious plan, will Ben face facts in time to blow them away?

added.title: Digital Quality
added.description: Ben and Gwen don't want to go to the CD Library. CDs are for old people. Ew. Once Team Tennyson is there, Lord Decibel traps them inside and demands a ransom. Ben and Gwen find Kevin inside on a potentially nefarious quest of his own, but it turns out that Lord Decibel may have already found the item that they so desperately desire.

added.title: Tim Buk-TV
added.description: Team Tennyson heads to the Okefenokee Swamp to witness the blooming of the Blushing Orchid, something that happens once every one hundred years. But their plans get disrupted when Tim Buk-Tu, trying to make his new 'reality' show more exciting, endangers the rare flower and everyone else at the swamp.

added.title: Growing Up is Hard to Do
added.description: Ben and Gwen are stoked to enter a skating competition, but when Nanny Nightmare shows up to teach the skater kids some manners by turning them into babies, it's up to Team Tennyson to up their game if they are to have any chance at saving the day.

added.title: The Hex Factor
added.description: When Hex mistakes an exclusive magic club for a top-secret Wizard society that snubbed him, Ben has to figure out how to work around the club's strict code of conduct to stop him without getting booted by security.

added.title: Legend of Torbaclaun
added.description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

added.title: Meet Tanya Keys
added.description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

added.title: Sand Trap
added.description: Axel and the team take to the desert dunes of a playground sandbox as Madcap attempts to unearth an army of Spy Lizards from the same line as Galileo!

added.title: Dodge City
added.description: Axel embraces the spirit of dodgeball to stop Madcap and Princess SugarSalt's battle over who is the better villain from spilling over into Zoe and Cleo's argument over who is the better coach!

added.title: The Loop Part 2
added.description: After escaping The Loop, Hot Rod, Clobber and Perceptor must stay one step ahead of their terrifying pursuers.

added.title: The Dead End Part 1
added.description: When Clobber enters the Deception Loop to rescue Lockdown, she attracts the attention of a different Decepticon instead.

added.title: The Dead End Part 2
added.description: Hot Rod and Clobber attempt to convince a disoriented and distrustful Dead End to join them in their fight against the Quintessons.

added.title: The Loop Part 1
added.description: It's a beautiful day on Cybertron and only Hot Rod doesn't seem to be enjoying the festive Parade of Metals.

added.title: El Otro Lado
added.description: Craig, Kelsey y JP deben viajar a través del Puente y aventurarse hacia el territorio no explorado del Otro Lado del Arroyo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Kelsey la autora
added.description: iCraig y Stacks ayudan a Kelsey a convertirse en una verdadera autora al convertir su historia en un libro!
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Primo del Arroyo
added.description: Craig lleva a su primo Bryson al Arroyo, donde accidentalmente inicia una guerra de globos de agua.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Campista Profuga
added.description: Una fugitiva de un campamento de verano termina en el Tronco, pero Craig sospecha que su historia puede no ser lo que parece.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Evolucion de Craig
added.description: iCraig rescata a un renacuajo y decide criarlo hasta que sea una rana nivel 100!
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Guarderia del Arroyo
added.description: Craig y su hermana Jessica intentan administrar la guarderia del Arroyo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Pequena Escuela Madre
added.description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

added.title: Consejos
added.description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

added.title: Capullos de Rosa
added.description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

added.title: Voleibol
added.description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

added.title: Azulejo
added.description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

added.title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
added.description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

added.title: Dia de Nevada
added.description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

added.title: Porque tan triste?
added.description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

added.title: Pequena graduacion
added.description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

added.title: Duo Espinoso
added.description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

added.title: #LaConvencionDeGotham
added.description: Un divertido día para Barbara Gordon y su mejor amiga Harley Quinzel en la Convención Anual de Gotham City, es puesto cabeza abajo cuando, de la nada, ila malvada Harley Quinn aparece para sembrar el caos! Por suerte para todos, Batgirl se encuentra casualmente en el área...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Despedidos
added.description: Los Fantásticos confrontan a Filomena, preocupados de que ella controle la energía de la Célula núcleo, y son despedidos de una forma poco profesional.

added.title: La batalla decisiva
added.description: Luego de que la Célula Núcleo pusiera en estado de hibernación a los Bakugan de ambos equipos, Dan y Magnus se encuentran atrapados en una batalla donde lo apostarán todo.

added.title: Perdiendo el control
added.description: Después de más intentos fallidos por aprovechar la energía la Célula núcleo, Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios Bakugan usando tecnología AAAnimus para salvarlos.

added.title: Un nuevo empleo
added.description: Durante un comercial para celebrar su contrato con el equipo AAAnimus, Dan y Los Fantásticos deciden rebelarse antes que traicionar sus principios.

added.title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 1
added.description: Los Fantásticos planean infiltrarse a AAAnimus para rescatar a sus Bakugan, pero Benton los detiene para ofrecerles un plan alternativo.

added.title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 2
added.description: Los Fantásticos unen fuerzas con Benton Dusk para rescatar a sus Bakugan y liberar la energía de la Célula Núcleo que AAAnimus tiene bajo su control.

added.title: Un experimento fallido
added.description: El plan de Filomena Dusk para redireccionar la energía de la Célula Núcleo fracasa, y Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios compañeros de trabajo dentro de las instalaciones de AAAnimus.

added.title: Un gran enfrentamiento
added.description: Lightning por fin revela la ubicación de la Célula Núcleo, pero cuando Los Fantásticos llegan, descubren que Magnus fue más rápido que ellos.

added.title: La aventura de Lightning
added.description: Lightning descubre la Célula Núcleo enterrada bajo tierra, y se enfrenta a Strata El Cazador para intentar proteger su secreto.

added.title: Un triunfo robado
added.description: Dan se embarca en una aventura para superar al nuevo equipo de Peleadores Bakugan de Magnus, pero al final, ellos lo salvarán a él.

added.title: Oportunidades laborales
added.description: Después de derrotar a Magnus, los Fantásticos reciben una oferta de empleo de alguien inesperado... Filomena Dusk.

added.title: Enemigos en el aire
added.description: Cuando Los Fantásticos transportan la Célula Núcleo a las instalaciones de AAAnimus, son atacados por Masato Kazami y sus Guardaespaldas.

removed.title: The Tooth About Zombies
removed.description: When Gwen's favorite event, the Zombie March, falls on the same day as Noah's nightmare event, dental hygienist check up day, Gwen and Noah find a way to help each other out.

removed.title: Once and for All
removed.description: Nya, Jay, Cole and Kai face off against the Ice Emperor's dreaded dragon, while Lloyd and his newfound allies, Kataru and Grimfax, confront the Ice Emperor himself.

removed.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
removed.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

removed.title: Arma de Eleccion
removed.description: Preocupado de que su espada sea un premio consuelo con pretensiones, Mao Mao decide salir a demostrar el valor de su arma.

removed.title: La Verdad Apesta
removed.description: Colosal huele mal, pero Mao Mao y Adorabat no saben cómo decírselo.
